<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Beautiful Desktop project</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Beautiful Desktop project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Beautiful Desktop</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Beautiful Desktop</em></p><article><p class="projects_first"><a href="http://www.beautiful-desktop.com/" target="_blank">Beautiful Desktop</a> is a personal project of mine that, as an amateur photographer and... wannabe entrepreneur, was the obvious culmination of those two aspirations.</p><p>The site offers free downloads of desktop wallpaper photos and acts as a creative outlet for my photography, but also as a potential source of revenue through Google AdSense. At least that was the idea. It's a more difficult goal to achieve than I had anticipated and as such, the process of running the site has taught me many valuable lessons.</p><p>Beautiful Desktop was developed using <a href="http://wordpress.org/" target="_blank">WordPress</a> and uses a premium theme which has some minor style modifications to it. It's several years old now and is perhaps due for a re-design. Still, time spent on it is better spent increasing traffic and optimising AdSense than overhauling the theme.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/bd/image_01_lge.jpg"><div id="project_lg" class="project"><img src="/images/works/projects/bd/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Beautiful Desktop home page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/bd/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/bd/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Beautfiul Desktop post detail"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section><ul><li><a href="http://www.beautiful-desktop.com/" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></li></ul></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>